title: Microsoft Office ProPlus 2013 SP1 VL x64 en-US May2015
description:
**************************************************************
*   Microsoft Office Professional Plus 2013 SP1 VL Channel   *
**************************************************************

Microsoft Office ProPlus 2013 SP1 VL x64 May2015
Contains SP1 and KB files currently needed as of May12-2015

Release File: Office-2013-SP1-PPVL-x64-en-US-May2015.iso
Size: 3.79 GB

Note:
For activation, use the Microsoft Toolkit 2.5.3 in the MTKV253.zip file.
MTK requires NetFX4, so if you are activating on Win7, you will need to
install the .NET Framework 4, 4.5, 4.5.1, or 4.5.2
Click the Office button, install AutoKMS, and click the Activate button.
If you experience a problem, try switching settings to use the TAP adapter
